mimm<u>a</u> razaqakumu All<u>a</u>hu wal<u>a</u> tattabiAAoo
khu<u>t</u>uw<u>a</u>ti a**l**shshay<u>ta</u>ni innahu lakum AAaduwwun
mubeen**un**

142\. Of the cattle are some  
For burden and some for meat:  
Eat what God hath provided  
For you, and follow not  
The footsteps of Satan:  
For he is to you  
An avowed enemy.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/006/006_143.gif)

143. Tham<u>a</u>niyata azw<u>a</u>jin mina a**l**<u>dd</u>a/ni ithnayni
wamina almaAAzi ithnayni qul <u>a</u>**l**<u>thth</u>akarayni
<u>h</u>arrama ami alonthayayni amm<u>a</u> ishtamalat AAalayhi
