<u>sa</u>diqeen**a**

143\. (Take) eight (head of cattle)  
In (four) pairs:  
Of sheep a pair,  
And of goats a pair;  
Say, hath He forbidden  
The two males,  
Or the two females,  
Or (the young) which the wombs  
Of the two females enclose?  
Tell me with knowledge  
If ye are truthful:

